<h2>The stuff I've done</h2>

<p>This is a simple gallerie of the different projects I've done so far. Some are not finished, some don't work the way I'd want but It's a good ego boost to keep a list of you I have achieved.</p>

{% for project in projects %}
<div class="project-card" onclick="window.open('{{project.demo_url}}')">
    <img class="project-img" src="../{{project.image}}" />
    <div class="text-overlay">
        <h3 class="project-title">{{project.name}}</h3>
        <p>{{project.description}}</p>
        <p>
        <a href="{{project.code_url}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Code</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
<br>
{% endfor %}
